Enable On-Screen Display shadow
Enables On-Screen Display shadow rendering. Shadow rendering can improve On-Screen Display readability in some applications by preventing the text from merging with solid screen color. 
Please take a note that shadow rendering increases performance hit caused by On-Screen Display rendering in vector modes, so enable it only when necessary.

